metricsWithGoal.goal: Keep the system simple and easy to change
metricsWithGoal.description: Aim at keeping the system size modest (less than 200,000 LOC is good), duplication low (less than 5% is good), files small (no files longer than 1000 LOC is good), and units simple (no units with more than 25 decision points is good).
